    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128080/extras/63b3654d732ca3fa3d76494a1d4b39c2.avif?t=1743166870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128080/extras_big/63b3654d732ca3fa3d76494a1d4b39c2.avif?t=1743166870 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Salvation 无尽救援：  </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款既包含双人合作解谜剧情，又包含单人解谜剧情的游戏。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>双人合作解谜，需要您找到一个同伴，各自购买一份游戏，进行解谜。</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <u>您和同伴无需联网！只需要能够交流即可，面对面、视频、电话交流都可以。</u></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双人合作游戏</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您和同伴分别扮演“拯救者”和“徘徊者”，分别在阳间、阴间，合计18个场景、83个画幅中合作解谜。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关后重复游玩二周目时，可以直接互换角色进行体验。谜底将有所区别。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>单人游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将扮演“拯救者”，在3个场景、12个画幅中进行解谜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人游戏剧情，是双人合作游戏的前置剧情。建议双人游戏之前，先行通关单人游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用横板移动，点击场景取得线索、对话、并解开谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全程只需使用鼠标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128080/extras/aff27c25e5335f24e20dc4d430c13e73.avif?t=1743166870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128080/extras_big/aff27c25e5335f24e20dc4d430c13e73.avif?t=1743166870 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
